            <h1 id="ministry-of-justice-representative-board-member">Ministry of Justice Representative Board Member</h1>
            <div class="govspeak">
<p>Liz Doherty joined the board of HM Courts & Tribunals Service as a representative of the Ministry of Justice in January 2016.</p>
